name: Ortlieb Pannier Commuter Insert
description: Bring order to the chaos of your pannier. This drop-in organizer has compartments for a laptop, water bottles and other small personal items.Tapered design suits Bike-Packer, Back Roller, and Velo-Shopper models.Large main compartment with padded laptop sleeve.2 organizer pockets, with key clip.Water bottle pocket.Rigid non-tipping design.Grab handle.
